    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I searched for this and found many answers to default value for column.If you want to use default value defined in SQL Table then in @Column Annotation use <strong><em>\"insertable = false\"</em></strong>. insertable </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>@Column(name = columnName, length = lengthOfColumn, insertable = false)</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>If you are using columnDefination it @Column annotation may be it won't work as it is Database dependent.</p>\n"
  }, {
