    "body" : "<p>Use hibernate annotation.</p>\n<pre><code>@ColumnDefault(&quot;-1&quot;)\nprivate Long clientId;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Recreate the table if it already exists for the changes to take effect.</p>\n"
