    "question_id" : 3110266,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you want to set default value in terms of database, just set <code>@Column( columnDefinition = \"int default 1\")</code></p>\n\n<p>But if what you intend is to set a default value in your java app you can set it on your class attribute like this: <code>private Integer attribute = 1;</code></p>\n"
