    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>i'am working with hibernate 5 and postgres, and this worked form me. </p>\n\n<pre><code>@Column(name = \"ACCOUNT_TYPE\", ***nullable***=false, columnDefinition=\"varchar2 default 'END_USER'\")\n@Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)\nprivate AccountType accountType;\n</code></pre>\n"
