    "body" : "<p>we can have getter that annotates @Column</p>\n<p>all @column should be annotated in getter alone instead of direct variable declaration. by this way, we can resolve it.</p>\n<pre><code>    @Column(name = &quot;string_value&quot;)\npublic String getStringValue(){\n         return (this.stringValue == null) ? &quot;Default&quot; : stringValue;\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
